thread.title_full: Pixels Logo Design reviewed by Ron Guidry

author: Ron Guidry
title: Ron Guidry
text:
Pixels Logo Design did a great job with web design and artwork. They worked with me on the design I wanted and implemented design changes very timely.
Isabella was great to work with. She coordinated the final changes very efficiently. She made the process very pleasant.
